left to right direction

actor "学校管理员" as Admin
actor "系统" as System

usecase "告警配置" as UC1
usecase "告警触发与通知" as UC2
usecase "告警历史查询" as UC3
usecase "告警规则编辑" as UC4

Admin --> UC1
